好几个不回答问题，反而阴阳我本人的，这里是我抽空写的一些解答，如果没有解决你们的问题，还请见谅： ①首先，非常感谢你对于此问题的持续关注。 ②其次，我提问这一问题的想法，就是期望有人，能够站在生物几十亿年来的演化（注意，不是进化）角度上，对此问题给予一定的答案。而这一角度，网上并没有我想要的相关讨论，所以我才来到人才辈出的知乎提问。 ③我是文科生，作为一名大学生，我必须首先研究自己专业范围内的相关知识，不可能去花费海量的时间去研究这种过于跨学科的知识，即使我有兴趣。 ④这个问题在我看来并非是无用的、吃饱了撑得，它能为我计划中的人生项目（如关于自动化运筹系统：“电筹”的毕业论文、以及我小说的世界观铺垫）打下基础。 ⑤回怼、阴阳，不符合我的三观，我会尽力克制自己去做，请大家放心。"},"attached_info":"Cj4IzPeR5u/99cd/EAMaCDc0NzEyODI5IO6z4I0GMAQ4eUAZcgk1MDU5NDExNzh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"74 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-e08f3f5be48ae6af343747d0297d2d58_720w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"26_1640009374.9181495","card_id":"Q_506433890","target":{"id":506433890,"title":"如何评价 10 月新番动画《国王排名》第十集？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/506433890","type":"question","created":1639633766,"answer_count":28,"follower_count":43,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[128,4650,7763,212252,726186],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"周五更新"},"attached_info":"Cj4IzPeR5u/99cd/EAMaCDc0ODIyNDk2IOam640GMAA4K0Aacgk1MDY0MzM4OTB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"72 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-a484f551cee72f530845d8a6671c0a09_720w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"27_1640009374.9186652","card_id":"Q_497298434","target":{"id":497298434,"title":"冬至文案怎么写呢？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/497298434","type":"question","created":1636282841,"answer_count":108,"follower_count":130,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[9014,60751,285235,586499],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IzPeR5u/99cd/EAMaCDcy